de Bacchus couronn\u00e9 de feuilles de vigne, deux paysans se prosternant devant la d\u00e9esse (l\u0027un portant une pelle et l\u0027autre un b\u00e2ton). Frise de la carrure repr\u00e9sentant Minerve et L\u00e9da au milieu de rinceaux. Cercle horaire \u00e0 chiffres romains se d\u00e9tachant sur une plaque grav\u00e9e de rinceaux peupl\u00e9s d\u0027oiseaux, de lapins, de deux Amours musiciens ; au centre, saint Antoine et ses cochons. Echappement \u00e0 verge, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet reperc\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de rinceaux fleuris.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Charles Peyras\/ABloys","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"6,6","displayDimension":"6,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,5","displayDimension":"2,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Blois (Centre-\u003ELoir-et-Cher = Loir et Cher)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Gavet ; collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"19\/06\/1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"}],"p